			<div class="content" id="post-content-2124116">
									

<p>So yeah. He's watching a movie starring <strong>Marshall</strong> Mathers, switches to an interview with Jimmy <strong>Carter</strong>, and ends on a show about being afraid of the <strong>Dark</strong>.</p>
<p>Too subtle? Maybe.</p>
<p>This was inspired by a chat comment about how MC&amp;D just doesn't do advertising right, and how they just sell shit. So I thought up &quot;The Ad-Man&quot;, an entity who does work like this for them.</p>
