&quot;Not the Cold War anymore, people are not so paranoid about TV anymore. Anyhow, ready for the report?&quot;<br />
&quot;Shoot.&quot;<br />
&quot;Foster, Phillip; loyalty check thirty-nine, scheduled internal security test. Subject did not pass. Recommending amnestization and immediate demotion to Level 0, if possible to a position with familial benefits.&quot;<br />
&quot;Softie. Checked in, twenty twelve, clearance level 4, Internal Security administration&#8230; that it?&quot;<br />
&quot;Yep. I'll leave you to it.&quot;</p>
</blockquote>

